Uh-oh. It's Superman. Superman.

1029
00:55:18,481 --> 00:55:22,068
But then the phone rang,
and it was Vince McMahon.

1030
00:55:22,152 --> 00:55:24,696
And he goes, "I need you to come home."

1031
00:55:24,779 --> 00:55:26,948
I said, "I've heard that before."

1032
00:55:28,033 --> 00:55:29,409
I said, "What's going on?"

1033
