He goes, "I need you because I know
how hot you are as Hollywood Hogan."

1034
00:55:32,871 --> 00:55:34,706
I said, "You finally admit it, huh?"

1035
00:55:36,166 --> 00:55:39,586
And Vince wanted me to wrestle
The Rock at WrestleMania.

1036
00:55:40,587 --> 00:55:45,633
How do you feel about headlining
one more WrestleMania with The Rock?

1037
00:55:45,717 --> 00:55:48,511
I said, "That's pretty darn interesting."

1038
00:55:48,595 --> 00:55:51,264
At that time, The Rock was on fire.

1039
00:55:51,348 --> 00:55:53,016
He hadn't made any movies yet,

1040
00:55:53,099 --> 00:55:55,477
but he was peaking
as far as his wrestling career.

1041
00:55:55,560 --> 00:55:57,687
If you smell…

1042
00:56:00,148 --> 00:56:03,318
…what The Rock is cookin'.

1043
00:56:06,112 --> 00:56:09,199
People also tell me
I look like a sexy Rob Schneider.

1044
00:56:10,617 --> 00:56:14,704
It was icon versus icon. Hulk versus Rock.

1045
00:56:14,788 --> 00:56:17,499
And it was a natural.

1046
00:56:17,582 --> 00:56:22,087
It'll be a pleasure
to kick your ass at WrestleMania.

1047
00:56:22,170 --> 00:56:25,006
I was feeling like I had accomplished

1048
00:56:25,090 --> 00:56:28,009
everything I wanted to accomplish
in wrestling.

1049
00:56:28,093 --> 00:56:30,845
And then the idea
of Hulk Hogan coming back,

1050
00:56:30,929 --> 00:56:36,101
it was the opportunity to create
something that was once in a lifetime.

1051
00:56:36,184 --> 00:56:38,061
Everything is a calculated risk with me.

1052
00:56:38,144 --> 00:56:40,939
You can say,
"Do I have enough left for another run?"

1053
00:56:41,022 --> 00:56:43,817
Hulk Hogan is attacking midlife
with a headlock.

1054
00:56:43,900 --> 00:56:47,278
The superstar
is climbing back into the ring.

1055
00:56:47,362 --> 00:56:51,199
Going into WrestleMania X8,
I was hurt two weeks before, really bad.

1056
00:56:51,282 --> 00:56:54,661
They shot me up with five doses
of lidocaine during the day.

1057
00:56:54,744 --> 00:56:57,080
They shot me up with Toradol.

1058
00:56:57,163 --> 00:57:00,917
The doctor says, "You won't feel a thing."
Yeah, right.

1059
00:57:01,501 --> 00:57:07,632
Welcome, ladies and gentlemen
around the world, to WrestleMania X8.

1060
00:57:11,594 --> 00:57:13,054
WrestleMania X8,

1061
00:57:13,138 --> 00:57:17,350
I will go on record, it's the greatest
WrestleMania match of all time.

1062
00:57:17,434 --> 00:57:19,310
It's the greatest match of all time.

1063
00:57:21,646 --> 00:57:24,107
It's simple. It's a story of the old lion,

1064
00:57:24,899 --> 00:57:26,151
the young lion.

1065
00:57:27,318 --> 00:57:32,740
Two iconic wrestlers
during their generational run.

1066
00:57:32,824 --> 00:57:37,078
And with me stacking
multi-generations on top of my legacy.

1067
00:57:38,371 --> 00:57:41,124
Many of the crowd chanting for The Rock.

1068
00:57:41,207 --> 00:57:44,711
He was a big Hulkamaniac as a young man.

1069
00:57:47,046 --> 00:57:49,132
The place was erupting.

1070
00:58:06,816 --> 00:58:10,612
And I realized,
they're cheering me instead of him.

1071
00:58:11,905 --> 00:58:14,073
They're supposed to love Rock.
Even Vince said,

1072
00:58:14,157 --> 00:58:17,327
"Hulk, they'll boo you tonight."
He said, "Okay."

1073
00:58:21,956 --> 00:58:25,210
But as soon
as he started punching me, "Boo!"

1074
00:58:30,423 --> 00:58:32,675
Here's what's great
about the wrestling fans.

1075
00:58:32,759 --> 00:58:35,094
Any given night, anything can change.

1076
00:58:39,599 --> 00:58:42,185
The audience is in total control, bro.

1077
00:58:42,268 --> 00:58:44,646
You surrender,
let the audience tell you what to do.

1078
00:58:44,729 --> 00:58:48,316
Hogan! Hogan! Hogan!

1079
00:58:57,075 --> 00:58:58,660
It was a poetry in motion.

1080
00:58:58,743 --> 00:59:01,871
Even The Rock said
it's the greatest match he's ever had.

1081
00:59:02,789 --> 00:59:08,336
One of the most incredible
nights I've ever had in my career.

1082
00:59:08,419 --> 00:59:10,922
He's gonna beat The Rock! Oh my God!

1083
00:59:11,005 --> 00:59:13,299
-Two…
-There's a two! And three!

1084
00:59:14,008 --> 00:59:17,720
The Brahma Bull kicked out!
Got his shoulder up.

1085
00:59:17,804 --> 00:59:20,223
There's a Rock drop.

1086
