There's a Rock Bottom on Hogan.
A hook of the leg.

1087
00:59:23,351 --> 00:59:25,478
-And this… Hogan kicked out!
-No!

1088
00:59:25,562 --> 00:59:28,523
-My God, Hogan kicked out.
-Look at this!

1089
00:59:28,606 --> 00:59:30,316
The Rock can't believe it.

1090
00:59:30,400 --> 00:59:34,946
Wait a minute.
Is he gonna Hulk up JR? He is!

1091
00:59:35,029 --> 00:59:37,240
Rock cannot believe it!

1092
00:59:38,700 --> 00:59:43,413
Every single soul in the entire building
was alive in that moment.

1093
00:59:43,496 --> 00:59:46,749
-What'll you do, Rock?
-Rock can't believe it!

1094
00:59:46,833 --> 00:59:48,585
What are you gonna do?

1095
