And Hulk scores the right hand.

1096
00:59:54,007 --> 00:59:56,843
Hogan’s setting The Rock up for the ride!

1097
00:59:56,926 --> 01:00:02,140
I felt like I slammed the Giant
and won the belt in Madison Square Garden.

1098
01:00:02,223 --> 01:00:08,313
You can see him so happy that,
"Hey, they're…"

1099
01:00:08,396 --> 01:00:09,981
"That's for me."

1100
