He beat Andre the Giant
with that move! The leg is hooked and…

1103
01:00:22,327 --> 01:00:26,039
Oh my God! My God, The Rock kicked out!

1104
01:00:42,472 --> 01:00:43,765
Hogan!

1105
01:00:43,848 --> 01:00:46,184
He's held on, but Hogan…

1106
01:00:49,270 --> 01:00:51,522
The Rock got the one, two, three
and beat me.

1107
01:00:51,606 --> 01:00:54,025
But I actually won the match

1108
01:00:54,108 --> 01:00:57,236
because it put me back on the map
in a major way.

1109
