Terry somehow got lost along the trip.

1130
01:02:42,133 --> 01:02:44,886
I trusted in Hulk Hogan
to the promised land

1131
01:02:44,969 --> 01:02:46,137
and to a higher level.

1132
01:02:46,220 --> 01:02:48,097
There's nothing they can do to Hulk Hogan.

1133
01:02:48,681 --> 01:02:50,099
State your name.

1134
01:02:50,183 --> 01:02:51,267
Terry Gene Bollea.

1135
01:02:51,350 --> 01:02:52,727
What is wrong with you?

1136
01:02:52,810 --> 01:02:55,772
The reality show
was kind of a recipe for disaster.

1137
01:02:55,855 --> 01:02:58,941
It was just years and years
of craziness and drama.

1138
01:03:00,735 --> 01:03:02,862
Enough was enough!

1139
01:03:02,945 --> 01:03:06,282
If I could reset it
now that I know exactly how it ended,

1140
01:03:06,365 --> 01:03:10,119
I would change
everything to the end of WrestleMania X8.

1141
01:03:10,703 --> 01:03:15,249
Fuck you, Hogan! Fuck you, Hogan!

